{"tid":1463858,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"應該增加第六大訴求，減少每日單程證人數，一年有4.4萬人黎香港","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:33:20.000Z","uid":127451,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ffabfec54077e8e5f03ab0561653e8f98cc143a8","tid":1463858,"uid":127451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:55:06.000Z","msg":"政府統計處公佈最新人口數字，今年年中本港人口數字為752.4萬人，較去年同期增加7.3萬人，增長率為1%，而常住人口則佔731萬。<br />\n<br />\n人口增長主要分為自然增長（即出生人數減去死亡人數）以及淨遷移（即移入人數減移出人數），2018年至2019年中人口自然增長為5700人，淨遷移人數為6.74萬，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中4.4萬為單程證持有人</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190813/59929035\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190813%2F59929035&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BjFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=919432e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190813%2F59929035&h=94f02fdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190813/59929035</a><br />\n<br />\n首先，我唔歧視新移民，有部分新移民黎香港的確係好勤力，但亦有部分黎香港無幾耐就領綜援，無論係邊種類都好，的確係會佔用唔少公共資源。<br />\n一年有4.4萬人批黎香港，但係公屋一年邊有4.4萬個，根據房署數字，2018至19年公屋+居屋落成量得26,779，供不應求，仲有對醫療，社會福利等其他資源都造成極大壓力，加上內地經濟愈來愈差，擔心更多人會用不同方法申請黎香港，再係咁，香港會陸沉，人均睇病時間只會愈黎愈長。<br />\n<br />\n房屋落成數字 <a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/about-us/publications-and-statistics/actual-public-rental-housing-production/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout-us%2Fpublications-and-statistics%2Factual-public-rental-housing-production%2Findex.html&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BjFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=77dd3b23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/about-us/publications-and-statistics/actual-public-rental-housing-production/index.html</a>)"},{"pid":"5026b31c0a970f6a90d79630e4721c3db3ce2640","tid":1463858,"uid":127451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5f056e2127a293307fa0c1b789869eab74b173a","tid":1463858,"uid":68471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:58:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"2bd89ddb50f665c640462128859f9c33d974435c","tid":1463858,"uid":62270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:58:55.000Z","msg":"直頭禁止啦"},{"pid":"cd6ca5c7710edec09687c9afbc01a9dbc82ec840","tid":1463858,"uid":127451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bd89ddb50f665c640462128859f9c33d974435c","tid":1463858,"uid":62270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:58:55.000Z","msg":"直頭禁止啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:00:53.000Z","msg":"禁晒冇人肯做粗重工作，除非肯用外勞"},{"pid":"0db2979a4bbbdf688dcae39933d374288137edca","tid":1463858,"uid":127451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:09:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"55426b34a1c36701524413867549205611285857","tid":1463858,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:33:20.000Z","msg":"有雙普選自然就得架啦"}]}